1
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,360
You can

2
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,720
transform into human form

3
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:31,840
and leave Yaochi.

4
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:34,960
Do you want to spend

5
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:37,640
more time after you go ashore?

6
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,680
What's your name?

7
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:43,000
Are you lost?

8
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:54,840
I grant you 500 years of magic power

9
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:58,560
to avenge the humiliation of our Jiao Snake clan

10
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,960
and pull out the Dinghai Needle.

11
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,640
My name is Xuanheng.

12
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,840
From now on,

13
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:09,880
you will be called

14
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:11,320
Xuanqing.

15
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,160
Later,

16
00:02:57,640 --> 00:03:00,120
I spent more and more time on shore,

17
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:04,160
and became increasingly curious about the Dinghai Divine Needle.

18
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:06,520
I wanted to eradicate it bit by bit.

19
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,600
Unexpectedly,

20
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,760
I angered the Queen Mother.

21
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:14,220
She later sent a divine official to suppress me.

22
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,360
That divine official was you,

23
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,960
Lu Sinian.

24
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,170
As for the rest of the story,

25
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:25,240
you all remember it.

26
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,720
But in your story,

27
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,400
there is no me.

28
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,240
Xuanqing.

29
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,440
You stopped halfway

30
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:38,290
and actually developed mortal feelings.

31
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,600
Don't forget.

32
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:43,000
She is an immortal.

33
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,200
You

34
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:47,040
are just a water monster after all.

35
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:51,160
Soul Transfer Spell.

36
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,200
Xuanqing,

37
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,839
I'll give you one more chance.

38
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:20,800
Don't let me down again.

39
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:23,360
I still let the Ancestor down.

40
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,000
After I was sealed,

41
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,640
the Ancestor told me that

42
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:31,720
the only chance to stop you

43
00:04:32,159 --> 00:04:34,800
is during your 99th reincarnation.

44
00:04:35,159 --> 00:04:37,400
I must absorb your Love God spirits

45
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:39,700
and pull out the Sea-Calming Needle.

46
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,360
Xuanqing.

47
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,280
Perhaps

48
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,090
I understand your Ancestor

49
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,520
better than you do.

50
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:51,760
He is just using you.

51
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,140
Whether I'm being used

52
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:55,680
or it's a trade,

53
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,720
how will I know if I don't try?

54
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,700
The Ancestor promised me that

55
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,360
when he is reborn next time,

56
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,000
he will let Yuyao and me be together.

57
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:06,920
Xuanqing,

58
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,600
they are lying to you.

59
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,240
The Gate of Rebirth

60
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:17,440
cannot be easily opened.

61
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,520
Yuyao,

62
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:24,140
while you waited for Lu Sinian through his 99 reincarnations,

63
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,090
I waited for you underwater

64
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:28,400
for 99 lifetimes as well.

65
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,280
Did you know that?

66
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,640
You didn't.

67
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,560
Yuyao.

68
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:10,760
Seeing you again after rebirth.

69
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:13,360
In this life.

70
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,800
Farewell forever.

71
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,159
Yu... Yuyao.

72
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,240
Sinian.

73
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,360
Sinian.

74
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:47,840
Yuyao.

75
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,400
I'm sorry

76
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,180
for keeping you

77
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,490
waiting so long.

78
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:00,640
I...

79
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,000
I

80
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,240
love...

81
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,360
love

82
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,120
you.

83
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:14,000
Sinian, wake up. Sinian.

84
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:17,040
Aren't you a heavenly official?

85
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,850
Aren't you capable of everything?

86
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,520
Wake up.

87
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:28,080
We were so close.

88
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,960
Just a little bit more,

89
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:33,320
and we could have been together forever.

90
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,200
Sinian,

91
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:37,840
wake up.

92
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,320
Sinian!

93
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:43,800
Sinian!

94
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:08,080
Why?

95
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:09,320
Why

96
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:11,570
can they sacrifice their lives

97
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,320
for each other?

98
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,640
Is this what love is?

99
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,200
Why?

100
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,760
Xuanqing.

101
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,640
The moon is full.

102
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,240
The formation is about to fail.

103
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:27,360
Pull out the Sea-Calming Needle

104
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:29,960
and set me free.

105
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:32,760
Since

106
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,500
you can't bring yourself to do it,

107
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:38,559
let me help you.

108
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,040
Yuyao.

109
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,240
Thank you

110
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,720
for making me understand

111
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,320
what

112
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,800
true love is.

113
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,320
Xuanqing.

114
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:07,120
You actually fell in love with a mortal,

115
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,600
for this woman,

116
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:10,840
and betrayed the Serpent Family.

117
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:12,760
Xuanqing.

118
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:32,960
Yuyao.

119
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:37,760
Yuyao.

120
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:41,360
Xuanqing.

121
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,160
Sinian.

122
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:00,880
I won't let you die.

123
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:03,960
No matter what it takes,

124
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,760
I will definitely save you.

125
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:08,330
Let's go.

126
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,080
Let's go home.

127
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,080
From today on,

128
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:37,320
you will manage Yaochi for me.

129
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,640
I grant you the name

130
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:39,600
Yuyao.

131
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:41,920
You must not neglect your duties

132
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:44,200
or develop mortal emotions.

133
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,480
Thank you, Queen Mother.

134
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:48,640
Considering your merit in suppressing demons,

135
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:50,570
But you harbored mortal feelings.

136
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,800
From this day on,

137
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:54,640
you will be banished to the mortal realm

138
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:57,360
to endure ninety-nine cycles of reincarnation

139
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:59,290
and experience mortal suffering.

140
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,120
As for Yuyao,

141
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:03,440
she will continue to guard the Jade Pool.

142
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,840
Without being summoned,

143
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:07,490
she shall never return to the heavenly realm.

144
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,440
Sinian.

145
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,050
Thousands of years ago,

146
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,040
to save me,

147
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,810
you stole the snow lotus

148
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:20,700
and willingly accepted the punishment.

149
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:22,360
Without being summoned,

150
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:25,330
I cannot ascend to the heavenly realm.

151
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,360
But you can.

152
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:30,800
Now, only the Queen Mother can save you.

153
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:34,680
As long as we climb these ninety-nine heavenly steps,

154
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:36,120
we still have a chance.

155
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,160
Did you hear me?
